  "readGuide": {
    "title": "How to read this",
    "api": {
      "name": "getDepositReconciliationReadGuide",
      "endpoint": "/api/v1/financials/trends-forecast/deposit-reconciliation/read-guide"
    },
    "points": [
      "📌 **Banner** auto-summarizes the largest mover, year-over-year change, and aging health each time the page loads.",
      "**Hero tile dots** are HFMA-style benchmarks: green = healthy, orange = watch, red = action. Hover for thresholds.",
      "**Aging waterfall** shows how long unmatched cash has been sitting. Industry target: keep > 30 days under 15%.",
      "**Compare toggle** switches the Δ column between MoM (latest vs prior month) and YoY (latest vs same month last year). YoY normalizes seasonality.",
      "**Trend** column shows the row's full trajectory across actual + forecast months. The dot marks the most recent actual.",
      "**Forecast columns** (italic, dashed border) project a 3-month trailing average forward. Swap in a real model when revenue planning gets in scope.",
      "**Data pending** badges mark rows whose underlying source is empty in this environment (PIP allocation, CAP liability, recoupments). The structure is reserved so the layout stays stable when those land.",
      "Hover any cell for the exact dollar figure."
    ]
  }
